title: Talks Machina: Discussing C1E83 - The Deceiver's Stand
description: Featured guest Sully joins Laura Bailey, Ashley Johnson, Taliesin Jaffe, Marisha Ray, and Brian Wayne Foster for Talks Machina! They discuss the previous episode of Critical Role, show some fan art, and give away a prize!
